<h1>Your MapMyData estimate is ready</h1>

<p style="color:#5E5E5E; font-size: 13px;">Hi <%= @order.name %>!</p>
<p style="color:#5E5E5E; font-size: 13px;">We finished analyzing the data you provided and this is the final estimate:</p>

<strong style="font-size: 17px; color:#333;black">Order #123456</strong>

<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">

  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 0 0 10px 0; font-size:15px; color: #666666;" width="180" valign="top"><%= @order.template.name.capitalize %> map</td>
    <td width="150" valign="top" style="text-align:right; padding: 0 0 10px 0; color: #E67632;"><%= @order.template.price %> USD</td>
  </tr> 

  <% @order.order_options.each do |o| %>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;">
      <td style="padding: 0 0 10px 0; font-size:15px; color: #666666;" width="180" valign="top"><%= o.template_option.name.humanize %></td>
      <td width="150" valign="top" style="text-align:right; padding: 0 0 10px 0; color: #E67632;"><%= o.template_option.price %> USD</td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>

  <% if @order.total - @order.starting_from > 0 %>
    <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;">
      <td style="padding: 0 0 10px 0;" width="180" valign="top"><strong style="font-size:17px">Additional</strong></td>
      <td width="150" valign="top" style="text-align:right; padding: 0 0 10px 0; color: #E67632;"><span style="font-size:15px; color: #E67632;">Starting on <%= @order.total - @order.starting_from %> USD</span></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>


  <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid #CCCCCC;">
    <td width="200" valign="top"><strong style="padding: 10px 0; font-size:17px; color: #333333;">TOTAL</strong></td>
    <td width="150" valign="top" style="text-align:right; padding: 10px 0; color: #E67632;"><span style="font-size:15px; color: #E67632;"><%= @order.total %> USD</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="color:#5E5E5E; font-size: 13px;">Are you ok with this estimate</p>

<p><a href="http://mapme-staging.herokuapp.com/orders/<%= @order.friendly_id %>/payments/new" style="font-weight: bold; font-size:27px; color: #397DB8;">Order it now</a></p>

<p style="color:#5E5E5E; font-size: 13px;">If you have any kind of question about it, please reply this email with your comments and we will solve your doubts as soon as possible.</p>

